original_title: Big Time Wrestling - Return of The Dragon
overview: Big Time Wrestling hosted the return to the ring of wrestling legend Ricky ‘The Dragon’ Steamboat! Teaming with FTR in a six-man tag team match against Jay Lethal, Brock Anderson and a mystery opponent.  Also in action Briscoe Brothers, Rock ‘n’ Roll Express, Scott Steiner, Matt Hardy & Crowbar. Featuring appearances from wrestling legends.
title: Big Time Wrestling - Return of The Dragon
